Day 57: Print Environment Variables

Date: October 24, 2025
Overview
Managed environment variables in Kubernetes pods.
Key Concepts Learned

ConfigMaps
Environment variable injection
Pod configuration
Secret management basics

Commands Used
yamlenv:
- name: DATABASE_URL
  value: "mysql://db:3306"
- name: API_KEY
  valueFrom:
    configMapKeyRef:
      name: app-config
      key: api-key
Challenges Faced
Understanding ConfigMaps vs Secrets and when to use each.
